{"tid":1062681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓粉：韓國瑜𣎴選總統 不會含淚投票 會轉投其他人","createTime":"2019-03-15T09:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:01:24.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c70f0a20ec09a733c3e78b4292ac570f0ec60266","tid":1062681,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190315/1533662/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190315%2F1533662%2F&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1249611c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190315%2F1533662%2F&h=0c002587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190315/1533662/</a><br />\n<br />\n前立委蔡正元力挺高雄市長韓國瑜參選總統，今天蔡正元又在臉書貼文表示，「非韓不投」這個韓流現象，已經是2020最重要的政治力量，若國民黨看不出這風潮，韓粉轉投台北市長柯文哲，國民黨必敗；蔡正元也將矛頭指向前總統馬英九、國安會前秘書長金溥聰，批評兩人挺新北市前市長朱立倫是有派系利益。"}]}